#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Some parts of the service are offered under paid plans described on our pricing page. Fees are billed in advance, are non-refundable except where required by law, and may change with at least 30 days' notice before your next billing period. If you stop paying, we may downgrade your account to a free tier after a reasonable grace period."
